snippet.title: MVP OR WHAT! | JONATHAN IS BACK!! | BGMI!
snippet.description:
If you liked the Video don’t forget to Like, Share and Subscribe.

Hey Guys, 
Welcome to my Youtube Channel,
I'm Jonathan Amaral, you might know me as Jonathan Gaming.
I started my professional Esports Career competing in Pubg Mobile Championships (Now BGMI),
Since the start of my career, I have been consistent with my gameplay and always been working hard to achieve my goals via winning Domestic/Global Championships. 
"The only player you should try to be better than is the player you were yesterday."
I Stream BGMI regularly, I also enjoy playing Valorant and other fun games once in a while!
I upload videos regarding Tutorials for BGMI, Funny Highlights, Intense Fights, Crate Openings, Vlogs, etc.

snippet.description:
"The GOAT" (The Goofiest Of All Time) is a Tamil film that falls under the 'milking' genre. Staying true to the genre, Venkat Prabhu has given a compilation of 'brainrot reels' that tries to harvest nostalgia, disguised as a movie. Thalapathy, Ilaya Thalapathy, Ilalaya Thalapathy and Ilalalaya Thalapathy have played pivotal roles in this goofy ahh film.

snippet.description:

Well this generation has changed so much. Me and Shyam being a millennials but having GENZ friends gave us this insight about them. 
Hum bhi kahin na kahin GenZ ke saath rehke same harkatein karne lag gaye hai 😅
But this video is pure exaggeration, GenZ itne bhi danger nahi hote hai.  Please take it in a funny way only.

snippet.title: #PowerStar Pawan Singh | कजरा मोहब्बत वाला | Shilpi Raj | Kajra Mohabbat Wala | नया भोजपुरी गाना
snippet.description:
रउवा लोगन से निहोरा करा तानी  की अपनी सीट बेल्ट कसके बाँध लीजिये क्युकी पवन सिंह का नया गाना अब आप  सबके सामने पेश कर रहे है #KajraMohabbatWala |

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:  @SaregamaHumBhojpuri 

Credits:
Singer :- Pawan Singh,Shilpi Raj
Lyrics :- Ashutosh Tiwari
Music :- Priyanshu Singh 
Feat :- Subhashree Kar
Director & Choreographer :- Lakkie Vishwakarma 
DOP :- Yogesh Singh 
Editor :- Anand Kumar (Santu)
DI :- Rohit Singh 
Production :- Aakash Vishwakarma
Assistant choreographer:- Suresh Patel

तोहरा पसंदीदा गाना उपलब्ध बानी सब OTT प्लैट्फ़ॉर्म पर !
Wynk: https://tinyurl.com/3x4us5dr
Gaana: https://tinyurl.com/5xt4v56c
Hungama: https://tinyurl.com/yc3hkjds
Amazon: https://tinyurl.com/yxudxjpc
Jio Saavn: https://tinyurl.com/bdhjkmwd
Youtube Music: https://tinyurl.com/2pxxzvxn

Lyrics:

लड़का:- पहिन के सड़िया करिया रे,लाग तिया ऐशवरिया रे
चाल से एकरा लागता की दाल में बा कुछ काला...
लड़की:- कजरा मोहब्बत वाला अँखियों में ऐसा डाला कजरे ने लेली मेरी जान...हाय रे मैं तेरे कुर्बान
लड़का:- दुनिया है मेंरे पीछे लेकिन मैं तेरे पीछे अपना बना ले मेरी जान...हाय रे मैं तेरे कुर्बान


लड़का:- फूल नियन बा कोमल काया
हुस्न के जलवा सबपे छाया
हम त पागल हो गइनी रे,अइसन तोरा रूप के माया
लड़की:- मेरा झुमका लाखों का,मेरा ठुमका लाखों का
बाबू लाखों में ही आये काला सुरमा आँखों का
लड़का:- लचके जब कमरिया रे,हटे नाही नजरिया रे
आग लगावे तन में हमार मन भइल मतवाला
लड़की:- कजरा मोहब्बत वाला..........



लड़का:- पुरा शहर जाम भइल बा,आज रंगीला शाम भइल बा
प्यार में तोरा पड़ के नामवा,पवन के बदनाम भइल बा
लड़की:- मेरे गाल गुलाबी रे,मेरी चाल नबाबी रे
बोले आशु प्रियांशु मुझको नॉटी भाभी रे
लड़का:- सोलह साल उमरिया रे,मारे जान गुजरिया रे
टच करी त मुँह से एकरा निकले ला उ लाला..उ लाला
कजरा मोहब्बत वाला.....

हम त पागल हो गइनी रे,अइसन तोरा रूप के माया
लड़की:- मेरा झुमका लाखों का,मेरा ठुमका लाखों का
बाबू लाखों में ही आये काला सुरमा आँखों का
लड़का:- लचके जब कमरिया रे,हटे नाही नजरिया रे
आग लगावे तन में हमार मन भइल मतवाला
लड़की:- कजरा मोहब्बत वाला..........



लड़का:- पुरा शहर जाम भइल बा,आज रंगीला शाम भइल बा
प्यार में तोरा पड़ के नामवा,पवन के बदनाम भइल बा
लड़की:- मेरे गाल गुलाबी रे,मेरी चाल नबाबी रे
बोले आशु प्रियांशु मुझको नॉटी भाभी रे
लड़का:- सोलह साल उमरिया रे,मारे जान गुजरिया रे
टच करी त मुँह से एकरा निकले ला उ लाला..उ लाला
कजरा मोहब्बत वाला.....

snippet.title: VENOM: THE LAST DANCE - Trailer Countdown
snippet.description:
Since you asked nicely. 

The final #Venom: The Last Dance trailer drops this Thursday.

Visit our site: https://venom.movie/

Follow Us On Social:
https://www.facebook.com/VenomMovie
https://x.com/VenomMovie
https://www.instagram.com/venommovie
https://www.tiktok.com/@venommovie

Subscribe to the Sony Pictures YouTube Channel for more exclusive content: http://bit.ly/SonyPicsSubscribe 

In Venom: The Last Dance, Tom Hardy returns as Venom, one of Marvel’s greatest and most complex characters, for the final film in the trilogy. Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie's last dance.
 
Venom: The Last Dance stars Tom Hardy, Chiwetel Ejiofor, Juno Temple, Rhys Ifans, Peggy Lu, Alanna Ubach and Stephen Graham. The film is directed by Kelly Marcel from a screenplay she wrote, based on a story by Hardy and Marcel. The film is produced by Avi Arad, Matt Tolmach, Amy Pascal, Kelly Marcel, Tom Hardy and Hutch Parker.

snippet.title: Deva Shree Ganesha - 8K/4K Video | Ganpati Song | Agneepath | Priyanka Chopra | Hrithik Roshan
snippet.description:
Experience the divine energy and vibrant spirit of Ganesh Chaturthi with the mesmerizing 8K/4K video of "Deva Shree Ganesha" from the blockbuster movie Agneepath. 
 
#devashreeganesha #hrithikroshan #priyankachopra #agneepath #ajayatul #ajaygogavale #ganeshsongs #ganpatisongs #ganpatibappamorya 

Credits :
Song Title- Deva Shree Ganesha 
Movie- Agneepath (2012) 
Singer- Ajay Gogavale 
Lyrics- Amitabh Bhattacharya 
Music- Ajay-Atul

Song Lyrics :
Jwaala Si Jalti Hai Aankhon Mein Jiske Bhi
Dil Mein Tera Naam Hai
Parwah Hi Kya Uska Aarambh Kaisa Hai
Aur Kaisa Parinam Hai
Dharti Ambar Sitaare
Uski Nazarein Utaarein
Dar Bhi Us Se Daraa Re
Jiski Rakhwaliyan Re Karta Saya Tera
Deva Shree Ganesha (X8)

Ho Teri Bhakti Ka Vardan Hai
Jo Kamaye Wo Dhanwan Hai
Bin Kinaare Ki Kashti Hai Woh
Deva Tujhse Jo Anjaan Hai
Yoon To Mooshak Sawari Teri
Sab Pe Hai Peharedaari Teri
Paap Ki Aandhiyan Laakh Hon
Kabhi Jyoti Na Haari Teri
Apni Takdeer Ka Woh Khud Sikandar Hua Re
Bhool Ke Yeh Jahan Re Jis Kisi Ne Yahan Re
Saath Paaya Tera Hey
Deva Shree Ganesha X (8)

Ho Teri Dhooli Ka Teeka Kiye
Deva Jo Bhakt Tera Jiye
Use Amrit Ka Hai Moh Kya
Hans Ke Vish Ka Woh Pyaala Piye
Teri Mahima Ke Chhaya Tale
Kaal Ke Rath Ka Pahiya Chale
Ek Chingari Pratishodh Se
Khadi Raavan Ki Lanka Jale
Shatruon Ki Kataarein Ik Akele Se Haarein
Kan Bhi Parbat Hua Re, Shlok Ban Ke Jahan Re
Naam Aaya Tera Hey
Deva Shree Ganesha X (8)

Ganpati Bappa Moreya
Ghalin Lotangan Vandin Charan
Dolyani Pahin Rup Tujhe
Deva Preme Alingan Anande Pujin
Bhave Ovaleen Mhane Nama

Twameva Mata,Cha Phita Twameva
Twameva Bandhuscha Sakha Twamevaa....
Twameva Vidya,Dravinum Twameva
Twameva Sarvam Mama Deva Devaaa

Kayena Vacha Manasendriyenva
Buddhyatmana Va Prakritiswabhavat
Karoomi Yadhyath Sakalam Parasmai
Narayanayeti Samarpayami

Achyutam Keshavam Ramnarayanam
Krushanadamodaram Vasudevam Bhaje
Shridharam Madhavam Gopikavallabham
Janaki Nayakam Ramchandra Bhaje

Hare Raam Hare Raam
Raam Raam Hare Hareee
Hare Krishna Hare Krishna
Krishna Krishna Hare Hareee
Hare Raam Hare Raam
Raam Raam Hare Hareeee
Hare Krishna Hare Krishna
Krishna Krishna Hare Hareee

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 43 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 8th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Shafia Khan

From stunning interiors to breathtaking views, this property is a perfect blend of modern design and comfort. As we explore each corner, we'll discover what makes this apartment one of the most sought-after living spaces in the city.  Join us as we delve into the amenities and unique features that make this home stand out. Could this be the dream home worth shifting to Hyderabad for?

As we wrap up this tour of the magnificent 8-crore apartment in Hyderabad, i hope you enjoyed experiencing the luxury and beauty of this extraordinary space. Living in such a place would be a dream come true for anyone with its perfect combination of modern amenities, elegance, and a prime location in one of India's fastest growing cities. Whether you're thinking about making Hyderabad your new home or simply curious about the high end real estate market, this apartment certainly showcases the best of what the city has to offer.

snippet.title: விநாயகர் சதுர்த்தி சிறப்பு பாடல் | ஆவணி வந்தது | விநாயகர் பாடல்கள் | Avani Vanthathu | Vinayagar
snippet.description:
#vinayagarchathurthi #விநாயகர்சதுர்த்தி #vinayagarsongs #ganeshasong 
Symphony presents Vinayaga chaturthi special vinayagar songs 2024, tamil vinayagar songs, ganesha songs, pillaiyar songs, pillaiyarpatti vinayagar songs, tamil devotional songs | Onbathu Kolum Kaanungal
Sung by: T.L.Maharajan, Mahanadhi Shobana, Kovai Kamala, Seergazhi Sivachidambaram, Harini, Unnikrishnan, Veeramanidasan, Sakthidasan, Srihari
Music: Aravind, T.L.Maharajan, D.V.Ramani, Kanmaniraja, Pallavi H.Prakash, Kalyan | Anand, L.Krishnan, Ajay
Lyrics: Dr.Kiruthiya, Ulundurpettai Shanmugam, Nellai Bharathikanthan, Poovai Senguttuvan, Sriram Sharma, Karpagadasan
Executive Producer: Srihari
Produced by: Symphony Recording Co.,

விநாயகர் சதுர்த்தி சிறப்பு பாடல்கள் 2024, ஆவணி மாதம் சிறந்த விநாயகர் பாடல்கள் 2024, வினைகள் நீக்கும் விநாயகர் பாடல்கள், தமிழ் பக்தி பாடல்கள் | ஒன்பது கோளும் காணுங்கள்
பாடியவர்: டி.எல்.மகாராஜன், மகாநதி ஷோபனா, கோவை கமலா, சீர்காழி சிவசிதம்பரம், ஹரிணி, உன்னிகிருஷ்ணன், வீரமணிதாசன், சக்திதாசன், ஸ்ரீஹரி
இசை: அரவிந்த், டி.எல்.மகாராஜன், டி.வி.ரமணி, கண்மணி ராஜா, பல்லவி எச். பிரகாஷ், கல்யாண் | ஆனந்த், எல்.கிருஷ்ணன், அஜய்
பாடல்கள்: Dr.கிருதியா, உளுந்தூர்பேட்டை சண்முகம், நெல்லை பாரதிகாந்தன், பூவை செங்குட்டுவன், ஸ்ரீராம் சர்மா, கற்பகதாசன்
தயாரிப்பு மேற்பார்வை: ஸ்ரீஹரி
தயாரிப்பு: சிம்போனி ரிகார்டிங் கம்பெனி

The Songs included in this album can be selected by touching or clicking the timings at the beginning of that song:

00:00 Avani Vanthathu | ஆவணி வந்தது

07:20 Naatukottaiyin | நாட்டுக்கோட்டையின்

13:44 Avani Vanthathu | ஆவணி வந்தது

Jaan Nisar Episode 51 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 7th September 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 42 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 7th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Kinni Soni Official Video | Darshan Raval | Shruti S.| Gurpreet S. | Naushad Khan | Out Of Control
snippet.description:
#KinniSoni #DarshanRaval #ShrutiSharma #naushadkhan #OutOfControl #Newsong2024 #IndieMusicLabel  

Here’s the second track from Darshan Raval’s album 'Out of Control' – 'Kinni Soni', featuring Shruti Sharma. With Darshan’s powerful vocals and Gurpreet Saini’s sharp lyrics, this song dives headfirst into the wild and crazy side of love. It’s all about the uncontrollable emotions, passion, and that electric energy you feel when you're swept up in love. If you’re ready for a ride filled with pure madness, this one’s for you. Get ready to feel it all!

An E Positive Entertainment Production

snippet.title: Why 10% Americans Think Earth is FLAT? | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
🤖 Join the Master ChatGPT Course: https://academy.dhruvrathee.com/chatgpt
Learn to harness the power of ChatGPT to transform your life!
Use coupon code: FLAT40 for a 40% discount!

In this video, we explore the psychology and influence behind the flat Earth movement, examining figures like Mike Hughes, a daredevil whose rocket launches were funded by flat Earthers, and dissecting why so many people reject established science. With critical analysis of cognitive biases and key historical experiments, this video exposes how pseudoscience thrives in the age of social media. From early flat Earth literature to modern-day YouTube influencers like Mark Sargent, this video uncovers the layers of psychology and cognitive biases fueling the movement.

snippet.title: Taaza Khabar | Season 2 | Official Trailer | Hotstar Specials | Sept 27 | BB Ki Vines Productions
snippet.description:
Don't forget to watch the series "Taaza Khabar" starring Bhuvan Bam, streaming exclusively on Disney+ Hotstar! http://www.hotstar.com/1260127221

Karza aur gunah chukaane padhte hain! Kabhi kabhi marr ke bhi..

Vardaan ya shraap? Kismat ya mehnat? Jeevan ya maut?
Vasya ki kahani ka naya adhyay dekhiye Hotstar Specials Taaza Khabar Season 2 mein, streaming from September 27, only on Disney+ Hotstar.

Disney+ Hotstar's hit fantasy-drama series returns with Hotstar Specials presents Taaza Khabar Season 2, diving deeper into the consequences of Vasya's miraculous gift. Set against the gritty backdrop of Mumbai, this season promises to take viewers on an intense journey as Vasya grapples with the loss of his power and faces life-threatening challenges.

Directed by Himank Gaur and produced by Rohit Raj & Bhuvan Bam under BB Ki Vines Productions, the show continues to be penned by the talented writer duo Hussain Dalal & Abbas Dalal. Bhuvan Bam reprises his role as Vasant Gawde, joined by Shriya Pilgaonkar, Mahesh Manjrekar, Jaaved Jaaferi, Deven Bhojani, Shilpa Shukla, Prathmesh Parab, and Nitya Mathur in pivotal roles.

This season explores the thin line between blessing and curse as Vasya navigates a world where his actions have far-reaching consequences. With higher stakes and deeper emotional complexity, Taaza Khabar Season 2 promises to deliver a gripping tale of redemption, morality, and the human spirit's resilience in the face of adversity.

#TaazaKhabarSeason2 #BBKiVinesProductions #BhuvanBam

ABOUT:
Bhuvan Bam, a multi-talented artist, returns as Vasya in this thrilling new season. To stay updated with Bhuvan's journey and behind-the-scenes content, follow him on:

snippet.title: Ranveer Brar, Kunal Kapoor तो नहीं लेकिन… | Bristi Home Kitchen @BristiHomeKitchen  Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Bristi Gupta की प्रेरणादायक कहानी: लॉकडाउन के दौरान 9 दिनों में 3 लाख से 1 मिलियन सब्सक्राइबर्स तक का सफर 

आज के Josh Talks Video में मिलिए यूट्यूबर क्रिएटर Bristi Gupta (Bristi Home Kitchen) से जो अपनी प्रेरणादायक यात्रा साझा करती हैं, जिसमें उन्होंने लॉकडाउन के दौरान अपने यूट्यूब चैनल को सिर्फ नौ दिनों में 3 लाख से 1 मिलियन सब्सक्राइबर्स तक पहुँचाया। वह एक चौंकाने वाला क्षण याद करती हैं जब उनके भाई ने उन्हें बताया कि उनका चैनल हैक हो गया है, जिससे उनकी सारी कमाई खत्म हो गई।

Bristi अपने मध्यमवर्गीय परिवार के बारे में बताती हैं, जहाँ उनके पिता एक आटा मिल चलाते थे और उनकी माँ गृहिणी थीं। शुरुआत में, कैमरे के सामने बात करने में आत्मविश्वास की कमी के कारण उन्होंने अपनी आवाज़ के बिना केवल संगीत के साथ कुकिंग वीडियो बनाने का निर्णय लिया और 16 अगस्त 2018 को अपना पहला वीडियो अपलोड किया। व्यक्तिगत चुनौतियों, जैसे उनके पिता की बीमारी के बावजूद, उन्होंने हिम्मत नहीं हारी और अपने चैनल को बढ़ाते हुए लगभग चार महीनों में 1.2 मिलियन सब्सक्राइबर्स तक पहुँचाया। आज उनके 5.3 मिलियन से अधिक सब्सक्राइबर्स हैं और वह अपने चैनल पर फूड और केक की रेसिपी अपलोड करती हैं, जो सभी को बेहद पसंद आती हैं। 

उनकी कहानी दिखाती है कि कैसे एक महिला घर से काम करके भी अन्य महिलाओं को प्रेरित कर सकती है। शादी के बाद अपने सपने को पूरा करने वाली Bristi हर उस महिला के लिए एक आदर्श हैं, जो अपने सपनों को साकार करना चाहती है।

Bristi ने यह भी संदेश दिया है कि समाज के ताने और आलोचनाएं हमेशा आएंगी। लेकिन अगर हमारा उद्देश्य साफ है और हमारी मेहनत सच्ची है, तो हम हर आलोचना का जवाब अपने काम से दे सकते हैं। उन्होंने दिखाया कि एक साधारण घर की महिला भी बड़े सपने देख सकती है और उन्हें पूरा भी कर सकती है, चाहे परिस्थितियां कैसी भी हों।

In this video, YouTuber Bristi Gupta aka (Bristi Home Kitchen)  shares her inspiring journey of growing her YouTube channel from 300,000 to 1 million subscribers in just nine days during the lockdown. She recalls a shocking moment when her brother informed her that her channel was hacked, wiping out all her earnings.

 Bristi talks about her middle-class family, where her father ran a flour mill, and her mother was a homemaker. Initially lacking confidence to speak on camera, she decided to create cooking videos without her voice, using only music, and uploaded her first video on August 16, 2018. Despite personal challenges, including her father’s illness, she persevered and grew her channel to 1.2 million subscribers in just four months. 

Today, with over 5.3 million subscribers, Bristi uploads popular food and cake recipes on her channel, inspiring many. Her story demonstrates how a woman can work from home and inspire others, especially women striving to fulfill their dreams after marriage. Bristi is a role model for every woman seeking to turn her aspirations into reality.

Her Channel - @BristiHomeKitchen 

Timestamps:

0:30 - परिचय और पारिवारिक पृष्ठभूमि.
3:35 - YouTube चैनल शुरू करने की प्रेरणा.
4:50 - YouTube की यात्रा और उसके शुरुआती संघर्ष.
8:42 - 1 मिलियन सब्सक्राइबर तक पहुँचने का सफ़र.
10:21 -  चैनल हैक होने की कहानी.
11:38 - चैनल को वापस पाने और उसके बाद का संघर्ष.
14:44 - 5 मिलियन सब्सक्राइबर तक पहुंचने की कहानी.
17:33 - निष्कर्ष.
17:53 - आभार.

snippet.description:
#UkadhicheModak #kabitaskitchen 

Preparation time - 60 mins
No of modak - 25 (approx)

Ingredients:
Rice flour - 1 cups
Water -1.75 cups

For Stuffing :
Fresh coconut - 2 cups
Jaggery - 1 cup
Cardamom powder -1/2 tsp
Ghee -1 tsp

About Mithijhora : 
__________________________

The show's story revolves around the lives of three sisters, Raipurna, Nilanjana, and Srotoswini. Following the sudden demise of their father, Kingshuk, Rai takes over the role of the main breadwinner for the family. Vikram, their elder brother, has physical challenges. There's a beautiful sisterhood bond between Rai, Nilu, and Srot. Rai is motivated more by her love for her sibling than by her obligation to provide for her family, nevertheless she works hard to support them.

Episode 4184: Bal Abdul Ki Kahaani
--------------------------------------------------------
Abdul reveals to the Gokuldham residents the true, underlying reason behind his decision to sell his shop. Will they rally behind him and offer their unwavering support in this difficult situation?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4184 | 7 Sep 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Teaser
snippet.description:
Be There and Be Square. #MinecraftMovie - only in theaters 2025

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, “A Minecraft Movie,” directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time.

The film also stars Emma Myers (“Wednesday”), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (“The Color Purple”), Sebastian Eugene Hansen (“Just Mercy, “Lisey’s Story”), with Jennifer Coolidge.

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn’t just help you craft, it’s essential to one’s survival!  Four misfits—Garrett “The Garbage Man” Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)—find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination.  To get back home, they’ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black).  Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative…the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (“Ninety-Five Senses,” “Nacho Libre”) directed, with Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Olafsson and Vu Bui producing, and Todd Hallowell, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza, Jonathan Spaihts, Pete Chiappetta, Andrew Lary and Anthony Tittanegro executive producing.

The director’s creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (“127 Hours,” “Transformers: Rise of the Beasts”), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (“The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,” “The Meg”), editor James Thomas (“Pokémon: Detective Pikachu”, the “Borat” films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (“The Jungle Book,” “The Batman”), and costume designer Amanda Neale (“The Meg,” “What We Do in the Shadows”).  Casting is by Rachel Tenner.  The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (“Thor: Ragnarok,” the “LEGO®” movies).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Mojäng Aktiebolag Production, A Jared Hess Film, “A Minecraft Movie.”  The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

snippet.title: #VenkyAnil3 x #SVC58 Vinayaka Chavithi Special Video | Venkatesh | Anil Ravipudi | Dilraju
snippet.description:
Watch #VenkyAnil3 x #SVC58 Vinayaka Chavithi Special Video!!

The extensive schedule of Victory Venkatesh, blockbuster machine Anil Ravipudi’s new film #VenkyAnil03 made under the esteemed production house Sri Venkateswara Creations was wrapped up. In this 30+ days long schedule, the makers filmed crucial sequences involving the lead cast, songs, and also action part.

On the occasion, and also to wish everyone on Vinayaka Chaturthi, offering a glimpse into the cheerful atmosphere on set. The video captures the joy and camaraderie among the cast, with smiles all around, perfectly embodying Charlie Chaplin’s sentiment that, “a day without laughter is a day wasted.

#VenkyAnil3 is the Hattrick film under the collaboration of Victory #VenkateshDaggubati, Hit Machine Director #AnilRavipudi and Blockbuster Producers Dilraju and Shirish. Touted as an extraordinary triangular crime entertainer, revolving around three characters- the protagonist, his ex-girlfriend, and his excellent wife. Produced by Sri Venkateswara Creations on a massive scale.

Meenakshi Chaudhary and Aishwarya Rajesh are the heroines opposite Venkatesh. Music is composed by Bheems Ceciroleo, Cinematography by Sameer Reddy, Production Designing by A S Prakash. Regular Shoot begins soon and will be released grandly for SANKRANTHI 2025. 

Cast: Venkatesh Daggubati, Meenakshi Chaudhary, Aishwarya Rajesh, Upendra Limaye, Rajendra Prasad, Sai Kumar, Naresh, VT Ganesh, Muralidhar Goud, Pammi Sai, Sai Srinivas, Anand Raj, Chaitanya Jonnalagadda, Mahesh Balaraj, Pradeep Kabra, and Chitti etc.,

snippet.title: அமெரிக்கா தியேட்டரில் GOAT பார்க்கலாம் வாங்க | Theatre experience & Review
snippet.description:
Goat (Tamil Movie) - American Theater Experience & Review

Watching "Goat" in the U.S. was electrifying! The theater buzzed with excitement from a diverse audience and the energy was contagious as everyone cheered and reacted together, making it a fun and communal experience.

Review: "Goat" showcases Thalapathy Vijay in a phenomenal dual role, delivering a powerful and versatile performance that’s the heart of the film. He seamlessly switches between contrasting characters, adding depth and charisma that keeps viewers hooked. Yuvan Shankar Raja’s background score is a perfect blend, elevating every scene with pulsating beats that amplify the film's intensity and emotional core.

The screenplay is tight and engaging, with unexpected twists that keep the audience on their toes. Venkat Prabhu’s direction is spot-on, expertly balancing action, drama, and humor, making "Goat" a standout experience. While the pacing dips slightly in places, the combination of stellar performances, gripping storytelling, and an unforgettable BGM make "Goat" a must-watch!

Clicks and Cuts - Madhavan
Cuts & Animation - Kamal

snippet.title: मेरे Teacher बनने की कहानी - Kumar Gaurav Sir @UTKARSHCLASSES13 Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
आज के Josh Talks Hindi वीडियो में हम एक अद्वितीय प्रेरणा स्रोत, Kumar Gaurav Sir से मिलेंगे। Kumar Gaurav Sir की यात्रा कठिनाइयों से भरी रही, लेकिन उन्होंने कभी हार नहीं मानी और अपने सपनों को साकार किया।

Kumar Gaurav Sir का जन्म एक साधारण परिवार में हुआ था और आर्थिक स्थिति भी अच्छी नहीं थी। पढ़ाई के दौरान कई चुनौतियों का सामना करने के बावजूद, उन्होंने अपने सपनों को साकार करने के लिए मेहनत की। ट्यूशन पढ़ाकर अपने खर्चों को पूरा करते हुए, उन्होंने आगे बढ़ने की दिशा में कदम बढ़ाया।

अपनी पढ़ाई पूरी करने के बाद, Kumar Gaurav Sir ने Utkarsh में एक content writer के तौर पर काम करना शुरू किया। अपनी मेहनत और लगन से उन्होंने सबका दिल जीत लिया और बहुत जल्दी Utkarsh के शीर्ष शिक्षकों में शामिल हो गए। उनकी लेखन शैली और शिक्षण का तरीका छात्रों के लिए प्रेरणा का स्रोत बन गया।

Kumar Gaurav Sir की कहानी हमें यह सिखाती है कि कठिनाइयों और संघर्षों के बावजूद, अगर हम मेहनत और समर्पण के साथ अपने सपनों के पीछे दौड़ें, तो किसी भी लक्ष्य को प्राप्त किया जा सकता है। उनकी यात्रा हमें अपने जीवन में सकारात्मकता और दृढ़ता बनाए रखने की प्रेरणा देती है।

इस वीडियो को देखना न भूलें और Kumar Gaurav Sir की प्रेरणादायक कहानी से प्रेरित होकर अपने सपनों को साकार करने के लिए मेहनत करें।

In today’s Josh Talks Hindi video, we meet an incredible source of inspiration, Kumar Gaurav Sir. His journey has been full of challenges, but he never gave up and turned his dreams into reality.

Born into a humble family with limited financial resources, Kumar Gaurav Sir faced numerous obstacles throughout his education. Despite these hardships, he worked hard to pursue his dreams. To support himself financially, he started giving tuition classes and gradually moved forward.

After completing his education, Kumar Gaurav Sir joined Utkarsh as a content writer. Through his dedication and hard work, he quickly earned recognition and became one of the top teachers at Utkarsh. His writing skills and unique teaching methods became a source of inspiration for students.

Kumar Gaurav Sir's story teaches us that no matter how difficult life gets, with determination and persistence, any goal can be achieved. His journey encourages us to stay positive and keep moving forward, no matter the obstacles.

Don't miss this video and get inspired by Kumar Gaurav Sir's motivational story to work hard and make your dreams come true.
#kumargauravsir   #inspiration  #motivation  #joshtalkshindi  #successstory  #contentwriters  #teachingjourney  #dreams  #hardwork  #dedication #UTKARSHCLASSES13
@UTKARSHCLASSES13


Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHindi 

DISCLAIMER -
All of the views and work outside the pretext of the video of the speaker, are his/ her own, and Josh Talks, by any means, does not support them directly or indirectly and neither is it liable for it. Viewers are requested to use their own discretion while viewing the content and focus on the entirety of the story rather than finding inferences in its parts. Josh Talks by any means, does not further or amplify any specific ideology or propaganda.

snippet.title: New Clan Notice Board and Loot Changes - Clash of Clans Update!
snippet.description:
Sneak Peek 1 for the Clash of Clans Update bring Clan Notice Boards, Loot Changes and many QoL Improvements. Judo Sloth Gaming explains all of the information released today. Most notably the Loot Changes will increase the amount of resources you can farm. This is because the amount of loot you can lose from storages on defense is being adjusted. There are also many improvements being added in this update, such as adjustments to the Hard Mode, and expansion of the Tactical Overview feature. Be sure to subscribe for Sneak Peek number 2. Clash On!

es.description:
Adelanto #1 para la actualización de Clash of Clans trae tablones de anuncios de clanes, cambios de botín y muchas mejoras de Calidad de Vida. Judo Sloth Gaming explica toda la información publicada hoy. En particular, los cambios de botín aumentarán la cantidad de recursos que puedes obtener. Esto se debe a que se está ajustando la cantidad de botín que puedes perder de los almacenamientos en defensa. También se están agregando muchas mejoras en esta actualización, como ajustes al Modo Difícil y la expansión de la función Descripción General Táctica. Asegúrate de suscribirte para el Adelanto número 2. ¡Vamos a Clash!

Vídeo sugerido:
100 días de progreso con el Pase de Oro: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CuMG4XUOr9I

Únete a 'The Dojo' para obtener beneficios exclusivos al convertirte en miembro del canal YT de Judo Sloth Gaming: https://www.youtube.com/judosloth/join

snippet.title: Saiyaan Ki Bandook - Nawazuddin Siddiqui | Pranjal Dahiya |  Sonu Thukral | Renuka | B Praak | Jaani
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies proudly presents the fiercest song of the year, Saiyaan Ki Bandook. Featuring the legendary Nawazuddin Siddiqui in his boldest avatar yet, Pranjal Dahiya delivering a knockout performance, and Sonu Thukral and Renuka Panwar lending their powerhouse vocals. Jaani’s composition and lyrics, combined with B Praak’s intense music, bring the perfect mix of love, revenge, and drama to life. Directed by the bossman, Arvvindr S Khaira, Saiyaan Ki Bandook is a full-blown experience.

Listen to 'Saiyaan Ki Bandook'' on your favourite streaming platform - https://umgindia.lnk.to/SKB

Episode 4183: Bal Gopal Gokuldham Group
--------------------------------------------------------
The spotlight shines bright on Tapu Sena as they prepare to take on the ultimate challenge cracking the Matki. With the entire family and neighbourhood on edge, can this dynamic group pull it off?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4183 | 6 Sep 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
